This paper is about automatic speech recognition (ASR) model compression using reinforcement learning (RL). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SD (Sound), which deals with audio and speech processing. The paper also involves natural language processing (NLP) techniques, which suggests cs.CL (Computation and Language) as another likely category. The use of RL for optimization indicates cs.LG (Machine Learning) as a possible category. Additionally, the paper involves decision-making processes, which suggests cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as another possible category. Finally, the paper deals with optimization of a complex system, which suggests cs.SY (Systems and Control) as a less likely but still possible category.
